        <item>
            <title>1.6.8</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:16:42 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>25</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Redesigned chat UI to match Claude Desktop Code tab styling: white background, system-ui font with weight 430, antialiased font smoothing, dark gray links with underline, bold headings
- Improved inline code styling: SF Mono font, subtle border and background, proper border-radius
- Status bar now uses white background for visual consistency

### Bug Fixes
- Fixed `#claude-error` element always visible even when empty
- Fixed undefined `--app-secondary-foreground` CSS variable for tool name secondary text
- Fixed leftover SSH process wrapper persisting into local sessions after remote session
- Unified error display styling between HTML template and dynamic JS error injection
]]></description>
